@node Now_Then_Now_Then

Sometimes Matthew refuses to fire, other times he's trigger happy. I don't know what causes this at all.
Matthew's eyebrows are transparent.
It may or may not work on your system. This is because Backbone kind of ceased development in 1998. 
That doesn't mean it's crud or anything. Au contraire.* It really is great. 

Don't think there's anything else.

* I get a GCSE "A" in French. For what? Adding "Au Contraire" to the end of a sentence?
 Of the 1000 words or so I learnt for the exam, do I only remember about 50 now? Well, yes. 
I did my French GCSE oral on this game. Did you know that? No, of course you couldn't know.

